00:39:21,540 --> 00:39:23,960
[RADIO STATIC]

700
00:39:24,370 --> 00:39:25,500
OH.

701
00:39:25,710 --> 00:39:28,210
THANK YOU, SWEETIE.

702
00:39:31,920 --> 00:39:33,510
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU,

703
00:39:33,720 --> 00:39:35,220
BUT LET'S GO OUTSIDE.

704
00:39:35,430 --> 00:39:38,430
OH, SWEETIE, I'D LOVE TO,
BUT I'M REALLY LATE.

705
00:39:38,680 --> 00:39:41,140
WHAT'S YOUR RUSH?

706
00:39:41,640 --> 00:39:42,430
SURGERY.

707
00:39:42,640 --> 00:39:44,350
THERE WAS THAT ELEVATOR
DISASTER DOWNTOWN.

708
00:39:44,560 --> 00:39:45,810
IT WAS ON THE NEWS
LAST NIGHT.

709
00:39:46,020 --> 00:39:48,060
THIS CABLE JUST SNAPPED.
THIS ELEVATOR,

710
00:39:48,270 --> 00:39:50,440
