10 FLIGHTS.

711
00:39:50,650 --> 00:39:51,530
THE NON-UNION WORKERS.

712
00:39:51,730 --> 00:39:53,740
JUST MONSTERS.
YOU KNOW, THAT BUILDING,

713
00:39:53,940 --> 00:39:55,280
IT'S RIGHT NEXT DOOR
TO WHERE YOU WORK.

714
00:39:55,490 --> 00:39:57,360
CAN YOU IMAGINE IF YOU
HAD BEEN IN THERE?

715
00:39:57,570 --> 00:39:59,200
IT'S NOT EVEN WORTH
THINKING ABOUT.

716
00:39:59,410 --> 00:40:00,200
ANYWAY,
I HAVE AN AMPUTATION

717
00:40:00,410 --> 00:40:03,410
ON ONE OF THE YOUNG
WOMEN IN THAT ELEVATOR.

718
00:40:03,410 --> 00:40:04,580
SHE'S VERY YOUNG.

719
00:40:04,790 --> 00:40:05,460
IT'S VERY SAD.

720
00:40:05,660 --> 00:40:07,500
ANYWAY, WISH ME LUCK.

721
00:40:07,710 --> 00:40:10,420
I'LL CROSS MY FINGERS
FOR YOU.

722
00:40:48,580 --> 00:40:50,710
[BRAKES SQUEAL]

723
00:40:50,920 --> 00:40:53,300
UH, EXCUSE ME.
HI. EXCUSE ME.

724
00:40:53,500 --> 00:40:55,260
MAY I HELP YOU?

725
00:40:55,460 --> 00:40:55,760
OH, UH...

