00:40:55,960 --> 00:40:58,930
YES. I'M LOOKING FOR MY WIFE,
NURSE BURBANK.

727
00:41:00,220 --> 00:41:00,760
IT'S VERY IMPORTANT.

728
00:41:00,970 --> 00:41:03,390
I'M AFRAID THAT
THAT'S NOT POSSIBLE.

729
00:41:03,600 --> 00:41:04,640
SHE'S IN PRE-OP.

730
00:41:04,850 --> 00:41:06,270
SURE.

731
00:41:06,480 --> 00:41:08,140
OK, FINE.

732
00:41:08,350 --> 00:41:09,730
CAN YOU PASS ALONG A MESSAGE?

733
00:41:09,940 --> 00:41:10,560
I'LL TRY.

734
00:41:10,770 --> 00:41:12,400
CAN YOU TELL HER
I HAD TO GO TO FIJI

735
00:41:12,610 --> 00:41:14,230
AND THAT I'LL CALL HER
WHEN I GET THERE?

736
00:41:14,440 --> 00:41:17,190
WHEN YOU--
WHEN YOU GET TO FIJI?

737
00:41:17,440 --> 00:41:18,070
YOU GOT IT.

738
00:41:18,280 --> 00:41:20,780
FINE. I'LL TELL HER.

739
00:41:20,780 --> 00:41:23,240
THANK YOU SO MUCH.

740
00:41:48,730 --> 00:41:49,890
SORRY.

741
00:41:50,100 --> 00:41:52,400
IT'S OK.

742
00:41:58,150 --> 00:42:00,490
HE'S HERE.

743
00:42:00,990 --> 00:42:03,870
Meryl: I KNOW, I KNOW.
SHH, SHH, SHH.

744
00:42:04,200 --> 00:42:06,490
SCALPEL.

745
00:42:08,290 --> 00:42:10,540
AHEM.

746
00:42:11,330 --> 00:42:14,130
I'M NOW MAKING
MY PRIMARY INCISION

747
00:42:15,420 --> 00:42:18,000
JUST ABOVE THE RIGHT KNEE.

748
00:42:19,760 --> 00:42:22,090
[LOUD CLANG]

749
00:42:24,260 --> 00:42:25,180
NICELY DONE.

750
00:42:25,390 --> 00:42:28,140
THIS ISN'T
GOING TO BE PRETTY.

751
00:42:28,220 --> 00:42:30,810
IT'S JUST
BEAUTIFUL.

752
00:42:30,850 --> 00:42:32,270
BEAUTIFUL JOB.

753
00:42:32,480 --> 00:42:35,400
I'LL JUST LET SOMEONE ELSE
TIDY UP HERE.

754
00:42:59,840 --> 00:43:02,420
I'M SORRY TO KEEP YOU.

