00:56:02,790 --> 00:56:03,910
WHO HASN'T WANTED
TO BE SOMEBODY?

1011
00:56:04,120 --> 00:56:07,170
THIS IS DIFFERENT.
EVERYBODY SEEMS TO BE IN ON IT.

1012
00:56:12,050 --> 00:56:15,130
I'VE BEEN YOUR BEST FRIEND
SINCE WE WERE 7 YEARS OLD.

1013
00:56:15,760 --> 00:56:17,640
THE ONLY WAY YOU AND I EVER
MADE IT THROUGH SCHOOL

1014
00:56:17,840 --> 00:56:20,850
WAS BY CHEATING OFF
EACH OTHER'S TEST PAPERS.

1015
00:56:21,810 --> 00:56:24,430
JESUS, THEY WERE IDENTICAL.

1016
00:56:25,640 --> 00:56:28,480
BUT I ALWAYS FELT SAFE
KNOWING THAT.

1017
00:56:29,230 --> 00:56:30,900
'CAUSE WHATEVER
THE ANSWER WAS,

1018
00:56:31,110 --> 00:56:34,190
WE WERE RIGHT TOGETHER
AND WE WERE WRONG TOGETHER.

1019
00:56:35,740 --> 00:56:38,740
REMEMBER WHEN I STAYED UP
ALL NIGHT IN YOUR TENT

1020
00:56:38,990 --> 00:56:41,830
'CAUSE YOU WANTED
TO PLAY NORTH POLE?

1021
00:56:42,330 --> 00:56:43,660
AND I GOT PNEUMONIA?

1022
00:56:43,870 --> 00:56:45,500
[LAUGHING]

1023
00:56:45,710 --> 00:56:47,460
YOU REMEMBER THAT?

1024
00:56:47,670 --> 00:56:50,590
YOU WERE OUT OF SCHOOL
FOR ABOUT A MONTH.

1025
00:56:55,970 --> 00:56:59,010
YOU'RE THE CLOSEST THING
I EVER HAD TO A BROTHER.

1026
00:57:06,020 --> 00:57:08,230
I KNOW THAT THINGS...

1027
00:57:08,440 --> 00:57:10,900
HAVEN'T REALLY WORKED
OUT FOR EITHER OF US

1028
00:57:11,110 --> 00:57:13,900
LIKE WE USED TO
DREAM THEY WOULD.

1029
00:57:14,070 --> 00:57:14,860
I KNOW THAT FEELING,

1030
00:57:15,070 --> 00:57:18,030
WHEN IT'S LIKE EVERYTHING'S
SLIPPING AWAY...

1031
00:57:18,950 --> 00:57:20,700
YOU DON'T WANT
TO BELIEVE IT,

1032
00:57:20,910 --> 00:57:23,870
SO YOU LOOK FOR ANSWERS
SOMEWHERE ELSE, BUT...

1033
00:57:28,500 --> 00:57:29,290
WELL...

1034
00:57:29,500 --> 00:57:32,380
Christof:
BUT, WELL, THE POINT IS...

1035
00:57:33,420 --> 00:57:36,380
I'D GLADLY WALK IN FRONT
OF TRAFFIC FOR YOU.

1036
00:57:40,140 --> 00:57:41,640
Marlon: WELL...

1037
00:57:41,850 --> 00:57:43,260
THE POINT IS,
I WOULD GLADLY

1038
00:57:43,470 --> 00:57:45,930
STEP IN FRONT OF TRAFFIC
FOR YOU, TRUMAN.

1039
00:57:46,140 --> 00:57:49,100
AND THE LAST THING
I'D EVER DO IS LIE TO YOU.

1040
00:57:51,980 --> 00:57:54,940
AND THE LAST THING
THAT I WOULD EVER DO...

1041
00:57:57,990 --> 00:58:00,360
IS LIE TO YOU.

1042
00:58:02,280 --> 00:58:05,040
I MEAN, THINK ABOUT IT,
TRUMAN.

1043
00:58:05,080 --> 00:58:07,750
IF EVERYBODY
IS IN ON IT...

1044
00:58:08,960 --> 00:58:11,630
I'D HAVE TO BE
IN ON IT, TOO.

1045
00:58:20,340 --> 00:58:23,180
I'M NOT IN ON IT,
TRUMAN, BECAUSE...

1046
00:58:23,930 --> 00:58:26,390
THERE IS NO "IT."

1047
00:58:29,230 --> 00:58:32,150
YOU WERE RIGHT ABOUT
ONE THING, THOUGH.

1048
00:58:33,270 --> 00:58:35,150
WHAT'S THAT?

1049
00:58:35,360 --> 00:58:38,110
THE THING THAT
STARTED ALL THIS.

1050
00:58:52,920 --> 00:58:55,670
YEP. I FOUND HIM
FOR YOU, TRUMAN.

1051
00:58:56,340 --> 00:58:58,550
THAT'S WHY
I CAME BY TONIGHT.

1052
00:58:58,760 --> 00:59:01,680
I'M SURE HE'S GOT
QUITE A STORY TO TELL.

1053
00:59:05,970 --> 00:59:08,310
GO TO HIM.

1054
00:59:13,650 --> 00:59:15,400
EASY ON THE FOG.

1055
00:59:15,610 --> 00:59:16,940
[KEYBOARD CLICKING]

1056
00:59:17,150 --> 00:59:19,650
STAND BY, CRANE CAM.

1057
00:59:20,360 --> 00:59:22,700
CRANE CAM.

1058
00:59:29,540 --> 00:59:32,000
BUTTON CAM 3.

1059
00:59:42,840 --> 00:59:45,430
I NEVER STOPPED BELIEVING.

1060
00:59:48,470 --> 00:59:51,220
Christof:
AND WIDE, CURB CAM 8.

1061
00:59:52,230 --> 00:59:54,600
MY SON! OH!

1062
00:59:54,940 --> 00:59:56,350
MOVE IN
FOR A CLOSEUP?

1063
00:59:56,560 --> 00:59:58,940
NO, NO, NO.

1064
00:59:59,400 --> 01:00:02,150
MOVE BACK AND...
FADE UP MUSIC.

1065
01:00:03,200 --> 01:00:05,610
[MUSIC SWELLS]

1066
01:00:09,120 --> 01:00:11,120
AND NOW GO IN CLOSE.

1067
01:00:11,330 --> 01:00:13,960
ALL THOSE
YEARS WASTED.

1068
01:00:14,160 --> 01:00:16,880
I'LL MAKE IT UP
TO YOU, SON.

1069
01:00:17,630 --> 01:00:19,540
I SWEAR.

1070
01:00:19,750 --> 01:00:22,170
[MUSIC SWELLS]

1071
01:00:25,970 --> 01:00:28,220
DAD.

1072
01:00:28,930 --> 01:00:31,180
YES!

1073
01:00:32,270 --> 01:00:34,600
[LAUGHING]

1074
01:00:39,440 --> 01:00:40,730
BRAVO.

1075
01:00:40,940 --> 01:00:43,780
THAT WAS A REALLY GREAT
EXPERIENCE.

1076
01:00:43,990 --> 01:00:44,570
Tech:
CONGRATULATIONS.

1077
01:00:44,780 --> 01:00:46,700
OK, QUIET DOWN.
LET'S CONCENTRATE.

1078
01:00:46,910 --> 01:00:49,570
Chloe:
THAT WAS GOOD WORK.

1079
01:00:49,700 --> 01:00:49,870
WHOO!

1080
01:00:50,080 --> 01:00:51,910
Tech: LET'S GET
SOME CHAMPAGNE UP HERE.

1081
01:00:52,120 --> 01:00:53,620
CONGRATULATIONS.

1082
01:00:53,830 --> 01:00:55,790
Moses: BRILLIANT, CHRISTOF.
JUST BRILLIANT.

1083
01:00:56,000 --> 01:00:58,750
Roman:
IT JUST BROKE MY HEART.

1084
01:01:02,250 --> 01:01:03,800
WELL DONE, EVERYONE!

1085
01:01:04,010 --> 01:01:06,260
BRAVO!

1086
01:01:22,610 --> 01:01:25,610
Announcer: 1.7 BILLION
WERE THERE FOR HIS BIRTH.

1087
01:01:29,660 --> 01:01:32,620
220 COUNTRIES TUNED IN
FOR HIS FIRST STEP.

1088
01:01:33,160 --> 01:01:36,120
THE WORLD STOOD STILL
FOR THAT STOLEN KISS,

1089
01:01:37,750 --> 01:01:40,380
AND AS HE GREW,
SO DID THE TECHNOLOGY.

1090
01:01:40,580 --> 01:01:41,290
AN ENTIRE HUMAN LIFE

1091
01:01:41,500 --> 01:01:44,550
RECORDED ON AN INTRICATE
NETWORK OF HIDDEN CAMERAS

1092
01:01:44,880 --> 01:01:47,840
AND BROADCAST LIVE AND
UNEDITED 24 HOURS A DAY,

1093
01:01:48,720 --> 01:01:51,720
7 DAYS A WEEK TO AN AUDIENCE
AROUND THE GLOBE.

1094
01:01:52,800 --> 01:01:55,430
COMING TO YOU NOW
FROM SEAHAVEN ISLAND,

1095
01:01:55,640 --> 01:01:58,640
ENCLOSED IN THE LARGEST
STUDIO EVER CONSTRUCTED,

1096
01:01:59,310 --> 01:02:00,940
AND ALONG WITH
THE GREAT WALL OF CHINA,

1097
01:02:01,190 --> 01:02:04,320
ONE OF ONLY 2 MANMADE STRUCTURES
VISIBLE FROM SPACE,

1098
01:02:05,730 --> 01:02:08,360
NOW IN ITS 30th GREAT YEAR,

1099
01:02:09,360 --> 01:02:11,660
IT'S...

1100
01:02:14,990 --> 01:02:17,200
WHAT A WEEK IT'S BEEN.
I DON'T KNOW ABOUT YOU--

1101
01:02:17,410 --> 01:02:19,080
I WAS ON PINS AND NEEDLES
THE ENTIRE TIME.

1102
01:02:19,290 --> 01:02:22,380
HELLO AND GOOD EVENING.
I'M YOUR HOST MIKE MICHAELSON,

1103
01:02:22,750 --> 01:02:24,040
AND WELCOME TO  TRU-TALK,

1104
01:02:24,250 --> 01:02:25,960
OUR FORUM FOR ISSUES
GROWING OUT OF THE SHOW.

1105
01:02:26,170 --> 01:02:29,090
BUT TONIGHT,
SOMETHING VERY SPECIAL INDEED,

1106
01:02:29,630 --> 01:02:31,340
A RARE AND
EXCLUSIVE INTERVIEW

1107
01:02:31,550 --> 01:02:33,800
WITH THE SHOW'S
CONCEIVER AND CREATOR.

1108
01:02:34,010 --> 01:02:37,100
SO, COME WITH US NOW AS WE
GO LIVE TO THE LUNAR ROOM

1109
01:02:37,430 --> 01:02:40,390
ON THE 221st FLOOR
OF THE OMNI CAM ECHOSPHERE,

1110
01:02:40,940 --> 01:02:44,060
WHERE WE'LL FIND THE WORLD'S
GREATEST TELE-VISIONARY--

1111
01:02:45,070 --> 01:02:47,480
THE DESIGNER AND ARCHITECT
OF THE WORLD WITHIN A WORLD

1112
01:02:47,690 --> 01:02:50,490
THAT IS SEAHAVEN ISLAND--
CHRISTOF.

1113
01:02:50,570 --> 01:02:53,120
BEFORE WE BEGIN,
I'D LIKE TO THANK YOU

1114
01:02:53,320 --> 01:02:55,870
ON BEHALF OF OUR AUDIENCE
FOR GRANTING THIS INTERVIEW.

1115
01:02:56,080 --> 01:02:57,830
WE KNOW HOW DEMANDING
YOUR SCHEDULE IS,

1116
01:02:58,040 --> 01:03:01,160
AND WE ALL KNOW HOW JEALOUSLY
YOU GUARD YOUR PRIVACY.

1117
01:03:02,000 --> 01:03:04,710
THIS, SIR,
IS INDEED AN HONOR.

1118
01:03:04,920 --> 01:03:05,420
DON'T MENTION IT.

1119
01:03:05,630 --> 01:03:07,800
WELL, THE CATALYST FOR
THE RECENT DRAMATIC EVENTS

1120
01:03:08,000 --> 01:03:10,970
ON THE SHOW HAS BEEN
TRUMAN'S FATHER, KIRK,

1121
01:03:10,970 --> 01:03:12,430
AND HIS ATTEMPTS
TO INFILTRATE THE SHOW.

1122
01:03:12,630 --> 01:03:14,890
BUT BEFORE WE GET INTO THAT,
I THINK IT'S WORTH NOTING

1123
01:03:15,100 --> 01:03:18,270
THAT THIS IS NOT THE FIRST TIME
SOMEONE FROM THE OUTSIDE

1124
01:03:18,560 --> 01:03:19,640
HAS ATTEMPTED
TO REACH TRUMAN, IS IT?

1125
01:03:19,850 --> 01:03:22,270
Christof: WE HAVE HAD
CLOSE CALLS IN THE PAST.

1126
01:03:22,480 --> 01:03:25,150
Man: TRUMAN!
IT'S TELEVISION!

1127
01:03:25,440 --> 01:03:26,570
YES!

1128
01:03:26,770 --> 01:03:28,230
YES! I DID IT!

1129
01:03:28,440 --> 01:03:29,690
I'M ON  THE TRUMAN SHOW!

1130
01:03:29,900 --> 01:03:32,320
Mike: BUT THERE'S NEVER
BEEN ANYTHING TO COMPARE

1131
01:03:32,530 --> 01:03:33,910
WITH THIS MOST RECENT
BREACH IN SECURITY--

1132
01:03:34,110 --> 01:03:37,120
THE FIRST INTRUDER TO BE
A FORMER CAST MEMBER.

1133
01:03:38,370 --> 01:03:39,200
A DEAD ONE AT THAT.

1134
01:03:39,410 --> 01:03:42,410
GOTTA SAY, WRITING KIRK
BACK IN--MASTERSTROKE.

1135
01:03:43,170 --> 01:03:46,210
SINCE KIRK STARTED THIS
CRISIS IN TRUMAN'S LIFE,

1136
01:03:46,250 --> 01:03:49,300
I CAME TO THE CONCLUSION
THAT ONLY HE COULD END IT.

1137
01:03:49,590 --> 01:03:52,090
TRUMAN! TRUMAN! NO!

1138
01:03:52,380 --> 01:03:53,470
[CONSTRUCTION NOISES]

1139
01:03:53,680 --> 01:03:54,550
THAT'S OFF LIMITS!

1140
01:03:54,760 --> 01:03:55,760
WHY? WHAT'S
OVER THERE?

1141
01:03:55,970 --> 01:03:57,850
NOTHING. IT'S DANGEROUS.
THAT'S ALL.

1142
01:03:58,050 --> 01:03:59,770
YOU'VE GOT TO KNOW
YOUR LIMITATIONS, TRUMAN.

1143
01:03:59,970 --> 01:04:02,350
Mike: BUT LET'S REMIND
VIEWERS EXACTLY WHY

1144
01:04:02,560 --> 01:04:04,770
DAD WAS WRITTEN OUT
IN THE FIRST PLACE.

1145
01:04:04,980 --> 01:04:06,730
Christof: AS TRUMAN GREW UP,
WE WERE FORCED

1146
01:04:06,940 --> 01:04:09,940
TO MANUFACTURE WAYS
TO KEEP HIM ON THE ISLAND.

1147
01:04:10,400 --> 01:04:12,070
I'D LIKE TO BE
AN EXPLORER,

1148
01:04:12,280 --> 01:04:13,780
LIKE THE GREAT
MAGELLAN.

1149
01:04:13,990 --> 01:04:14,400
YOU'RE TOO LATE.

1150
01:04:14,610 --> 01:04:17,490
THERE'S REALLY
NOTHING LEFT TO EXPLORE.

1151
01:04:17,660 --> 01:04:19,990
[SNARLING]

1152
01:04:21,540 --> 01:04:24,620
Christof: FINALLY, I CAME UP
WITH KIRK'S DROWNING.

1153
01:04:24,620 --> 01:04:25,370
Mike: MOST EFFECTIVE.

1154
01:04:25,580 --> 01:04:27,250
TRUMAN'S BEEN TERRIFIED
OF THE WATER EVER SINCE.

1155
01:04:27,460 --> 01:04:30,550
Christof: WHEN KIRK READ
THE SYNOPSIS OF THE EPISODE,

1156
01:04:30,550 --> 01:04:33,470
HE WAS DISAPPOINTED
TO SAY THE LEAST.

1157
01:04:33,970 --> 01:04:34,130
JESUS!

1158
01:04:34,340 --> 01:04:37,470
I'M SURE THAT'S WHAT CAUSED
HIM TO BREAK ONTO THE SET.

1159
01:04:37,760 --> 01:04:40,850
BUT HOW DO YOU INTEND TO
EXPLAIN HIS 22-YEAR ABSENCE?

1160
01:04:43,350 --> 01:04:43,770
AMNESIA.

1161
01:04:43,980 --> 01:04:46,980
BRILLIANT. LET'S TAKE
SOME VIEWER PHONE CALLS.

1162
01:04:47,440 --> 01:04:50,520
CHARLOTTE, NORTH CAROLINA,
YOU'RE ON WITH CHRISTOF.

1163
01:04:51,190 --> 01:04:53,610
Man: UH, YEAH,
HI, CHRISTOF.

1164
01:04:53,820 --> 01:04:56,950
I WAS WONDERING HOW MANY
CAMERAS YOU GOT IN THAT TOWN.

1165
01:04:57,490 --> 01:04:59,570
SOMEWHERE IN
THE VICINITY OF 5,000.

1166
01:04:59,780 --> 01:05:02,290
Man: THAT'S
A LOT OF CAMERAS.

1167
01:05:02,490 --> 01:05:05,290
REMEMBER, WE STARTED
WITH JUST ONE.

1168
01:05:05,410 --> 01:05:08,080
HE WAS CURIOUS
FROM BIRTH.

1169
01:05:10,170 --> 01:05:11,000
PREMATURE BY 2 WEEKS.

1170
01:05:11,210 --> 01:05:12,960
ALMOST AS IF HE COULDN'T
WAIT TO GET STARTED.

1171
01:05:13,170 --> 01:05:16,130
Mike: HIS EAGERNESS
TO LEAVE HIS MOTHER'S WOMB

1172
01:05:16,510 --> 01:05:17,880
WAS THE VERY REASON
HE WAS THE ONE SELECTED.

1173
01:05:18,090 --> 01:05:20,640
IN COMPETITION WITH 5 OTHER
UNWANTED PREGNANCIES,

1174
01:05:20,850 --> 01:05:23,850
THE CASTING OF A SHOW,
DETERMINED BY AN AIR DATE,

1175
01:05:23,890 --> 01:05:26,770
TRUMAN WAS THE ONE
WHO ARRIVED ON CUE.

1176
01:05:30,940 --> 01:05:34,110
Mike: INCIDENTALLY, I BELIEVE
TRUMAN IS THE FIRST CHILD

1177
01:05:34,110 --> 01:05:36,320
TO HAVE BEEN LEGALLY ADOPTED
BY A CORPORATION.

1178
01:05:36,530 --> 01:05:37,570
THAT'S CORRECT.

1179
01:05:37,780 --> 01:05:39,780
THE SHOW HAS GENERATED
ENORMOUS REVENUES NOW,

1180
01:05:39,990 --> 01:05:43,240
EQUIVALENT TO THE GROSS NATIONAL
PRODUCT OF A SMALL COUNTRY.

1181
01:05:43,740 --> 01:05:45,370
PEOPLE FORGET IT TAKES
THE POPULATION

1182
01:05:45,580 --> 01:05:47,040
OF AN ENTIRE COUNTRY TO
KEEP THE SHOW RUNNING.

1183
01:05:47,250 --> 01:05:48,960
SINCE THE SHOW IS ON
24-HOURS A DAY

1184
01:05:49,170 --> 01:05:52,420
WITHOUT COMMERCIAL INTERRUPTION,
ALL THOSE STAGGERING REVENUES

1185
01:05:53,090 --> 01:05:55,010
ARE GENERATED
BY PRODUCT PLACEMENT.

1186
01:05:55,210 --> 01:05:57,590
THAT'S TRUE. EVERYTHING
ON THE SHOW IS FOR SALE.

1187
01:05:57,800 --> 01:05:59,180
FROM THE ACTOR'S WARDROBE,
FOOD PRODUCTS,

1188
01:05:59,380 --> 01:06:00,220
TO THE VERY HOMES
THEY LIVE IN.

1189
01:06:00,430 --> 01:06:03,560
Mike: AND ALL OF IT AVAILABLE
IN THE TRUMAN CATALOG.

1190
01:06:03,680 --> 01:06:05,020
OPERATORS ARE STANDING BY.

1191
01:06:05,220 --> 01:06:06,850
CHRISTOF, LET ME ASK YOU,

1192
01:06:07,060 --> 01:06:10,020
WHY DO YOU THINK TRUMAN
HAS NEVER COME CLOSE

1193
01:06:10,400 --> 01:06:13,480
TO DISCOVERING THE TRUE NATURE
OF HIS WORLD UNTIL NOW?

1194
01:06:13,770 --> 01:06:15,650
WE ACCEPT THE REALITY
OF THE WORLD

1195
01:06:15,860 --> 01:06:17,780
WITH WHICH WE ARE
PRESENTED.

1196
01:06:17,990 --> 01:06:20,070
IT'S AS SIMPLE AS THAT.

1197
01:06:20,280 --> 01:06:21,990
THE HAGUE FOR CHRISTOF.

1198
01:06:22,200 --> 01:06:24,660
HELLO? THE HAGUE?

1199
01:06:25,700 --> 01:06:26,790
ALL RIGHT,
WE'VE LOST THAT CALL.

1200
01:06:27,000 --> 01:06:28,960
LET'S GO TO HOLLYWOOD.
YOU'RE ON  TRU-TALK.

1201
01:06:29,160 --> 01:06:31,790
HI, CHRISTOF. I'D JUST
LIKE TO SAY ONE THING.

1202
01:06:32,000 --> 01:06:33,210
YOU'RE A LIAR
AND A MANIPULATOR,

1203
01:06:33,420 --> 01:06:35,300
AND WHAT YOU'VE DONE
TO TRUMAN IS SICK!

1204
01:06:35,500 --> 01:06:38,420
WELL, WE REMEMBER
THIS VOICE, DON'T WE?

1205
01:06:40,840 --> 01:06:41,840
HOW COULD WE FORGET?

1206
01:06:42,050 --> 01:06:43,350
Mike: LET'S GO
TO ANOTHER CALL.

1207
01:06:43,550 --> 01:06:46,220
NO, NO, NO.
IT'S FINE, MIKE.

1208
01:06:46,720 --> 01:06:49,810
I LOVE TO REMINISCE WITH
FORMER MEMBERS OF THE CAST.

1209
01:06:51,100 --> 01:06:53,060
SYLVIA...

1210
01:06:53,270 --> 01:06:56,320
AS YOU ANNOUNCED SO
MELODRAMATICALLY TO THE WORLD,

1211
01:06:56,650 --> 01:06:59,820
YOU THINK BECAUSE YOU BATTED
YOUR EYES AT TRUMAN ONCE...

1212
01:07:02,410 --> 01:07:04,030
FLIRTED WITH HIM...

1213
01:07:04,240 --> 01:07:05,580
STOLE A FEW MINUTES
OF AIR TIME WITH HIM...

1214
01:07:05,780 --> 01:07:09,000
TO THRUST YOURSELF AND YOUR
POLITICS INTO THE LIMELIGHT...

1215
01:07:09,910 --> 01:07:11,040
THAT YOU KNOW HIM?

1216
01:07:11,250 --> 01:07:13,040
THAT YOU KNOW
WHAT'S RIGHT FOR HIM?

1217
01:07:13,250 --> 01:07:16,340
YOU REALLY THINK YOU'RE
IN A POSITION TO JUDGE HIM?

1218
01:07:16,380 --> 01:07:18,420
WHAT RIGHT DO YOU HAVE
TO TAKE A BABY

1219
01:07:18,630 --> 01:07:21,590
AND TURN HIS LIFE INTO
SOME KIND OF MOCKERY?

1220
01:07:21,680 --> 01:07:24,300
DON'T YOU EVER
FEEL GUILTY?

1221
01:07:25,220 --> 01:07:28,270
I HAVE GIVEN TRUMAN A CHANCE
