WE'VE GOT THE LIGHT.

1490
01:21:15,090 --> 01:21:17,890
SO HE'S GOT TO
BE THERE SOMEWHERE.

1491
01:21:20,180 --> 01:21:21,350
WE'RE NOT
WATCHING THE SEA.

1492
01:21:21,560 --> 01:21:24,680
