WHY WOULD WE WATCH THE SEA?

1493
01:21:25,230 --> 01:21:26,310
SWEEP THE HARBOR.

1494
01:21:26,520 --> 01:21:27,270
BRING UP THE HARBOR CAMERAS.

1495
01:21:27,480 --> 01:21:30,020
SHIFT ALL HARBOR CAMERAS
TO COMPUTER, PLEASE.

1496
01:21:30,230 --> 01:21:31,780
