AREN'T THEY?

1497
01:21:31,980 --> 01:21:33,110
Operator: YEAH.
WE HAVE 4 OF THEM DOWN,

1498
01:21:33,320 --> 01:21:35,490
BUT WE HAVE
THE LIGHTHOUSE CAMERAS UP.

1499
