Operator: PAN IT,
WILL YOU, PLEASE?

1504
01:21:48,710 --> 01:21:51,040
TRUMAN...

1505
01:21:52,090 --> 01:21:54,550
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

1506
01:21:54,710 --> 01:21:56,720
