HE'S IN INSURANCE.

1507
01:21:56,930 --> 01:21:58,340
Operator: ISN'T HE
TERRIFIED OF THE WATER?

1508
01:21:58,550 --> 01:21:59,300
RESUME TRANSMISSION.

1509
01:21:59,510 --> 01:22:02,060
RESUMING TRANSMISSION.

