Man: HEY, I WANT
A PIECE OF THAT.

1512
01:22:10,230 --> 01:22:12,070
2 TO 1
HE DOESN'T MAKE IT.

1513
01:22:12,270 --> 01:22:13,690
[KEY TAPPING]

1514
01:22:13,900 --> 01:22:16,150
JUST LEAVE 'EM
IN THE CAR.

1515
01:22:16,360 --> 01:22:18,610
SHH.

1516
01:22:28,620 --> 01:22:29,920
LET'S GET OFF
THIS MAST SHOT.

1517
01:22:30,130 --> 01:22:32,500
