OF A TELEVISION SHOW

1586
01:32:29,600 --> 01:32:32,770
THAT GIVES HOPE AND JOY
AND INSPIRATION TO MILLIONS.

1587
01:32:38,320 --> 01:32:39,650
THEN WHO AM I?

1588
01:32:39,860 --> 01:32:42,280
YOU'RE THE STAR.

1589
01:32:47,580 --> 01:32:49,240
WAS NOTHING REAL?

1590
01:32:49,450 --> 01:32:50,250
YOU WERE REAL.

1591
01:32:50,450 --> 01:32:53,290
THAT'S WHAT MADE YOU
SO GOOD TO WATCH.

1592
01:32:54,290 --> 01:32:56,330
LISTEN TO ME, TRUMAN.

1593
01:32:56,540 --> 01:32:58,920
THERE'S NO MORE TRUTH
OUT THERE...

1594
01:32:59,130 --> 01:33:02,130
THAN THERE IS IN THE WORLD
I CREATED FOR YOU.

1595
01:33:04,680 --> 01:33:07,100
THE SAME LIES.

1596
01:33:08,050 --> 01:33:09,770
THE SAME DECEIT.

1597
01:33:09,970 --> 01:33:12,430
BUT IN MY WORLD...

1598
01:33:13,690 --> 01:33:16,310
YOU HAVE NOTHING
TO FEAR.

1599
01:33:18,110 --> 01:33:20,690
I KNOW YOU BETTER
THAN YOU KNOW YOURSELF.

1600
01:33:20,900 --> 01:33:23,700
YOU NEVER HAD
A CAMERA IN MY HEAD.

1601
01:33:25,490 --> 01:33:26,990
YOU'RE AFRAID.

1602
01:33:27,200 --> 01:33:29,870
THAT'S WHY
YOU CAN'T LEAVE.

1603
01:33:33,460 --> 01:33:35,870
IT'S OK, TRUMAN.

1604
01:33:37,250 --> 01:33:39,040
I UNDERSTAND.

1605
01:33:39,250 --> 01:33:42,170
I HAVE BEEN WATCHING YOU
