1606
01:33:44,550 --> 01:33:47,340
I WAS WATCHING
WHEN YOU WERE BORN.

1607
01:33:49,010 --> 01:33:51,970
I WAS WATCHING WHEN YOU
TOOK YOUR FIRST STEP.

1608
01:33:56,140 --> 01:33:59,110
