FIRST DAY OF SCHOOL.

1609
01:34:00,440 --> 01:34:01,270
[LAUGHS]

1610
01:34:01,480 --> 01:34:04,400
THE EPISODE WHEN YOU
LOST YOUR FIRST TOOTH.

1611
01:34:08,870 --> 01:34:11,410
YOU CAN'T LEAVE, TRUMAN.

1612
01:34:11,990 --> 01:34:13,330
PLEASE, GOD.

1613
01:34:13,540 --> 01:34:15,540
Christof:
YOU BELONG HERE...

1614
01:34:15,750 --> 01:34:18,130
YOU CAN DO IT.

1615
01:34:18,830 --> 01:34:21,130
WITH ME.

1616
01:34:22,420 --> 01:34:24,130
TALK TO ME.

1617
01:34:24,340 --> 01:34:26,720
SAY SOMETHING.

1618
01:34:29,260 --> 01:34:32,060
WELL, SAY SOMETHING,
GODDAMN IT.

1619
01:34:32,510 --> 01:34:33,310
YOU'RE ON TELEVISION.

1620
01:34:33,520 --> 01:34:36,270
YOU'RE LIVE
TO THE WHOLE WORLD.

1621
01:34:53,660 --> 01:34:56,000
