1622
01:34:56,200 --> 01:34:59,170
GOOD AFTERNOON, GOOD EVENING,
AND GOOD NIGHT.

1623
01:35:02,960 --> 01:35:05,170
YEP.

1624
01:35:25,480 --> 01:35:27,900
YEAH!
YEAH!

1625
01:35:31,030 --> 01:35:33,070
HE DID IT.
HE DID IT.

1626
01:35:33,280 --> 01:35:35,950
HE DID IT!
HE DID IT!

1627
01:35:37,870 --> 01:35:39,660
HE MADE IT! YEAH!

1628
01:35:39,870 --> 01:35:42,330
ALL RIGHT, TRUMAN!

1629
01:35:50,510 --> 01:35:51,340
CEASE TRANSMISSION.

1630
01:35:51,550 --> 01:35:53,180
CEASING
TRANSMISSION.

1631
01:35:53,390 --> 01:35:55,810
[TAPS KEYBOARD]

1632
01:35:57,970 --> 01:35:59,060
YOU WANT ANOTHER SLICE?

1633
01:35:59,270 --> 01:36:00,140
NO. I'M OK.

1634
01:36:00,350 --> 01:36:01,020
WHAT ELSE IS ON?

